comments: Holmgren (OKC) is actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Holmgren's (OKC) approaches Doncic (DAL) with his arms extended and the contact during his pass is marginal.
Lively II (DAL) briefly places a hand at Dort's (OKC) side and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Williams (OKC) taps the ball without control and then fumbles before it is touched by Lively II (DAL). Once he gains control, he legally starts his dribble.
Williams (OKC) steps with his right heel above the baseline without touching it on his drive.
Irving (DAL) brushes Williams' (OKC) left arm and the contact during the dunk is marginal.
Wallace (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position during Irving's (DAL) drive to the basket.
Irving (DAL) gathers the ball on his right foot with the ball against his side, and then takes three steps before releasing the pass.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes contact with the ball and the ensuing contact with Lively II's (DAL) hand is incidental.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) initiates illegal contact across Washington's (DAL) right arm in order to reach the ball.
Dort (OKC) steps out of bounds with his right foot while still in possession of the ball.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) brushes Williams' (OKC) left arm and the contact does not affect his layup attempt.
Holmgren (OKC) collapses his arm and legally contests Lively II's (DAL) shot attempt near the rim.
Lively II (DAL) and Holmgren (OKC) make incidental arm contact with each other as they pursue the loose ball.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) initiates illegal contact across Lively II's (DAL) arm before Dort (OKC) dislodges the ball away.
Jones Jr. (DAL) initiates illegal contact with Holgren (OKC) as he attempts to secure the rebound.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) places his off-arm against Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and releases away for the shot attempt.
Washington (DAL) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
When Dort (OKC) steps forward, he initiates contact to Doncic's (DAL) leg and foot, causing him to fall during the driving shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on Holmgren (OKC).
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on Washington (DAL) prior to the release of his pass.
Giddey (OKC) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
Washington (DAL) attempts to commit a take foul by stepping into Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).  Doncic does not make more than marginal contact when he attempts to foul Gilgeous-Alexander.
Washington (DAL) is called for a take foul for contact to Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) arm.
